        {
          "key": "journal_completion_guide",
          "value": {
            "speakerName": "Mayor Andrew",
            "text": "To complete your journal: 1) Catch all fish types in your catalog, 2) Debone each type to finish entries, 3) Keep the Population Health Meter healthy, and 4) Earn 2,000 gold. Balance fishing and processing.",
            "showAsAction": true,
            "showConditions": [],
            "triggersOnShow": [],
            "choices": [
              {
                "choiceText": "What about the 2,000 gold?",
                "resultDialogId": "tuition_reminder",
                "triggersOnShow": [],
                "showConditions": []
              },
              {
                "choiceText": "Back to main questions.",
                "resultDialogId": "post_market_default",
                "triggersOnShow": [],
                "showConditions": []
              }
            ],
            "nextDialogId": ""
          }
        },
        {
          "key": "tuition_reminder",
          "value": {
            "speakerName": "Mayor Andrew",
            "text": "The 2,000 gold tuition is separate from your journal. Sell quality fish and deboned fillets at the market. Higher quality = better prices. Remember: Skillful processing earns more.",
            "showAsAction": true,
            "showConditions": [],
            "triggersOnShow": [],
            "choices": [
              {
                "choiceText": "How do I complete my journal?",
                "resultDialogId": "journal_completion_guide",
                "triggersOnShow": [],
                "showConditions": []
              },
              {
                "choiceText": "Back to main questions.",
                "resultDialogId": "post_market_default",
                "triggersOnShow": [],
                "showConditions": []
              }
            ],
            "nextDialogId": ""
          }
        },
        {
          "key": "friendly_greeting",
          "value": {
            "speakerName": "Mayor Andrew",
            "text": "Good to see you! Keep balancing your fishing and processing. The community notices your responsible work.",
            "showAsAction": true,
            "showConditions": [],
            "triggersOnShow": [],
            "choices": [],
            "nextDialogId": ""
          }
        },
        {
          "key": "journal_review",
          "value": {
            "speakerName": "Mayor Andrew",
            "text": "Ah, there you are. Professor Clark and I have reviewed your Field Journal. You've made excellent progress. Your journal is complete, and I hear you have the 2,000 gold for tuition?",
            "showAsAction": true,
            "showConditions": [
              {
                "conditionType": 3,
                "conditionKey": "FIELD_JOURNAL_COMPLETE",
                "conditionValue": "COMPLETED"
              }
            ],
            "triggersOnShow": [],
            "choices": [
              {
                "choiceText": "Yes, I have the gold ready.",
                "resultDialogId": "graduation_decision",
                "triggersOnShow": [
                  "CheckGold:2000"
                ],
                "showConditions": []
              },
              {
                "choiceText": "Not yet, I need more time.",
                "resultDialogId": "not_ready_yet",
                "triggersOnShow": [],
                "showConditions": []
              }
            ],
            "nextDialogId": ""
          }
        },
        {
          "key": "graduation_decision",
          "value": {
            "speakerName": "Mayor Andrew",
            "text": "All requirements met! Your journal shows balance and skill. Now you must decide: graduate now or stay to perfect your work?",
            "showAsAction": true,
            "showConditions": [],
            "triggersOnShow": [],
            "choices": [
              {
                "choiceText": "I'm ready to graduate.",
                "resultDialogId": "graduate_now",
                "triggersOnShow": [],
                "showConditions": []
              },
              {
                "choiceText": "I want to stay and improve.",
                "resultDialogId": "stay_and_improve",
                "triggersOnShow": [],
                "showConditions": []
              },
              {
                "choiceText": "What's the difference?",
                "resultDialogId": "graduation_explanation",
                "triggersOnShow": [],
                "showConditions": []
              }
            ],
            "nextDialogId": ""
          }
        },
        {
          "key": "not_ready_yet",
          "value": {
            "speakerName": "Mayor Andrew",
            "text": "Take your time. A steward knows when to wait. Return when you have the 2,000 gold and feel your journal is truly complete.",
            "showAsAction": true,
            "showConditions": [],
            "triggersOnShow": [],
            "choices": [],
            "nextDialogId": ""
          }
        },
        {
          "key": "graduation_explanation",
          "value": {
            "speakerName": "Mayor Andrew",
            "text": "Graduate now: ceremony at Academy, receive stewardship title, tuition settled, work complete. Stay longer: improve skills, build reputation, perfect journal. There's no rush—choose when your story feels complete.",
            "showAsAction": true,
            "showConditions": [],
            "triggersOnShow": [],
            "choices": [
              {
                "choiceText": "I'm ready to graduate.",
                "resultDialogId": "graduate_now",
                "triggersOnShow": [],
                "showConditions": []
              },
              {
                "choiceText": "I want to stay and improve.",
                "resultDialogId": "stay_and_improve",
                "triggersOnShow": [],
                "showConditions": []
              },
              {
                "choiceText": "Back to decision.",
                "resultDialogId": "graduation_decision",
                "triggersOnShow": [],
                "showConditions": []
              }
            ],
            "nextDialogId": ""
          }
        },
        {
          "key": "graduate_now",
          "value": {
            "speakerName": "Mayor Andrew",
            "text": "Then it's my honor to accept your Stewardship Field Journal. You've become part of Riversong's story. Professor Clark is waiting at the Academy for your graduation.",
            "showAsAction": true,
            "showConditions": [],
            "triggersOnShow": [
              "StartQuest:GRADUATION_DAY"
            ],
            "choices": [],
            "nextDialogId": ""
          }
        },
        {
          "key": "stay_and_improve",
          "value": {
            "speakerName": "Mayor Andrew",
            "text": "I had a feeling you'd say that. A true steward is never fully satisfied. Continue your work—the water and community await. Return when your journal feels complete.",
            "showAsAction": true,
            "showConditions": [],
            "triggersOnShow": [],
            "choices": [],
            "nextDialogId": ""
          }
        },
